{"tid":1613523,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［職業解鎖］弓箭手","createTime":"2019-10-02T14:33:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T08:44:25.000Z","uid":325214,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"efc0ada96138d0fa7c0e2a22f9ed9e4213e2a752","tid":1613523,"uid":325214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T14:33:46.000Z","msg":"最近香城online副本越來越難打<br />\n稀有裝嘅掉落機率又低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且偽勇武嘅出現嚴重影響遊戲體驗<br />\n特別係10.1 超大型副本<br />\n多個server嘅玩家都深受體會<br />\n<br />\n有見及此 <br />\n喺到建議開放弓箭手<br />\n就算偽勇武企後少少<br />\n都唔會影響其他遊戲玩家體驗<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1. 射程遠 大約50米-100米 企後少少都唔會阻到前線<br />\n2. 反制速犬上黎咬<br />\n3. 箭頭可搭載不同魔法 如火魔法 毒魔法<br />\n<br />\n缺點：<br />\n1. 太顯眼 無得摺疊 普通背包未必放得落 裝弓嘅袋同wargame槍袋差不多咁長 可能未入副本組到隊友就被怪咬死<br />\n2. 唔容易上手 <br />\n<br />\nBtw 千奇唔好用弩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為香城online講明超過6公斤拉力嘅弩係會當外掛處理 直接停權ban ac<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n祝大家武運昌隆<br />\n早日爆機<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A4f03mb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA4f03mb.jpg&h=1deb5f1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6kuMY5M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6kuMY5M.jpg&h=dd9a8308&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9d7ff0076c021ed1fefd891ef5956b467edf2ba6","tid":1613523,"uid":60049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T14:37:59.000Z","msg":"Slingshot <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92d6692e963bee8215fce3f9093a4efbc2b5016d","tid":1613523,"uid":289624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d7ff0076c021ed1fefd891ef5956b467edf2ba6","tid":1613523,"uid":60049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019